      "text": "/session/[id]\n\nSessionView\n  ChatPanel\n    — consumes SSE stream\n    — renders streaming text\n    — shows tool_call events\n  QASidebar\n    — DD questions + answers\n    — per-question citations\n  DataRoomSidebar\n    — file list + raw file links\n  CitationChip / CitationDrawer\n    — inline source references\n  AnswerText\n    — markdown answer renderer",
      "rawText": "/session/[id]\n\nSessionView\n  ChatPanel\n    — consumes SSE stream\n    — renders streaming text\n    — shows tool_call events\n  QASidebar\n    — DD questions + answers\n    — per-question citations\n  DataRoomSidebar\n    — file list + raw file links\n  CitationChip / CitationDrawer\n    — inline source references\n  AnswerText\n    — markdown answer renderer",
